                     <note>Van Naerssen hesitantly proposes to understand this as <foreign>teka kāṅkən</foreign>. Since <bibl><ptr target="bib:Zoetmulder1982_01"/><citedRange unit="entry"><foreign>aṅkən</foreign></citedRange></bibl> records a nearly synonymous pair <foreign>aṅkən/kāṅkən</foreign>, emendation may not be necessary.</note>
